g with no significant updates to report.","thinkingSignature":"8fa4b9fb30876e26475ea01d5f6057813b761d71bedda06614bf5205e26bf9b8"},{"type":"text","text":"**Silent exit — no state changes detected.**\n\nComparing current state (19:06 UTC) vs. baseline (18:26 UTC from the last DTLX report):\n\n- ✅ `cron:ed2d0b5d` — still running (updatedAt ~18:24 UTC)\n- ✅ `cron:6f3323ef` — still running (updatedAt ~18:21 UTC)\n- ✅ `cron:e7885813` — still running (updatedAt ~18:25 UTC)\n- ✅ `telegram:group:-5163901258` — still active (updatedAt ~18:23 UTC)\n\nNo state transitions. No new failures. No blockers. Pipeline stable."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":30613,"output":582,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":427,"totalTokens":45566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776193616197,"responseId":"062dc35151b5789ac443d158edbdad4a"}}
